Project Xfire : Source Directory for Parallel Version
--------------------------------------------------------
by Josep Jorba @July 1998 CAOS-UAB

########################################################
#                  XFIRE INSTALLATION                  #
########################################################

Dependencies:
-------------

  -OpenMPI (>1.8.8)

Installation:
-------------

$ cd src/
$ ./configure
$ make

The XFire executable will be in the root directory
and in the same src/ folder with the name `xfire`. 

Demo executions:
----------------

$ mpirun -np 4 xfire demo
$ mpirun -np 4 xfire demo2

